/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the street and its surroundings. The street itself is lined with lush green trees, their leaves rustling gently in the breeze. Power lines crisscross above, forming a complex web against the backdrop of the clear blue sky. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades bathed in the soft glow of daylight. In the distance, a large body of water glistens under the sun, adding a serene touch to the urban landscape. The colors in the image are predominantly green, blue, and gray, painting a picture of a city where nature and architecture coexist harmoniously.
